doc.previous: The maiden flight of the Airbus A318 took place at Toulouse on 15 January 2002, and the first customer delivery was on 22 July 2003 to Frontier Airlines.[15] As of July 2013, 47 A318s remained in commercial service with 6 airlines.[16]
